World map backdrops — all NASA imagery, public domain, fetched directly
from NASA (no third-party application assets):

earth.jpg        NASA Blue Marble classic equirectangular, as shipped by
                 xplanet (/usr/share/xplanet/images/earth.jpg).
earth_veg.jpg    NASA Blue Marble Next Generation, July, with topography
                 and bathymetry (visibleearth.nasa.gov imagerecord 73751,
                 world.topo.bathy.200407), downscaled to 2700x1350.
earth_night.jpg  NASA Black Marble 2016 city lights (visibleearth
                 imagerecord 144898, BlackMarble_2016_01deg), 2700x1350.

Used for the panadapter map backgrounds with live grayline shading.
